The All Progressives Congress, APC, National Executive Council, NEC, meeting has commenced. The NEC meeting convened by embattled Deputy National Secretary of APC, Victor Giadom is holding at the Presidential Villa, Abuja. The meeting has in attendance President Muhammadu Buhari, Vice President, Yemi Osinbajo and some members of the APC National Working Committee, NWC. Buhari’s Personal Assistant on New Media, Bashir Ahmad made the disclosure in a tweet. “The National Executive Committee (NEC) of the ruling party, the APC has just commenced at the State House, Abuja. President Buhari, VP Osinbajo, Governors and members of the National Working Committee (NWC) of the Party and other members of the NEC are in attendance,” he tweeted. The National Executive Committee (NEC) of the ruling party, the APC has just commenced at the State House, Abuja. President Buhari, VP Osinbajo, Governors and members of the National Working Committee (NWC) of the Party and other members of the NEC are in attendance. pic.twitter.com/jQyk1TGqd0 — Bashir Ahmad (@BashirAhmaad) June 25, 2020